(42, 5, 6, 12, 4, 3, 7, NULL, 'Miraculous Provision of Abundance', 'This connection highlights the theme of miraculous provision in both passages. In Luke 5:6, the fishermen experience an overwhelming catch, while in 2 Kings 4:3-7, the widow''s oil multiplies to meet her needs.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 6, 21, 11, 6, 6, 'inclosed a great multitude of fishes', 'Connection of Abundance and Effort', 'This connection highlights the theme of diligent effort leading to unexpected abundance. Both passages emphasize the importance of sowing and working, with the outcome being uncertain but potentially fruitful.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 6, 48, 6, 9, 9, 'great multitude of fishes', 'Well Doing and Reaping', 'This connection highlights the theme of reaping rewards from diligent efforts. In Luke, the fishermen''s hard work results in a great catch, paralleling the encouragement in Galatians to persist in well doing for future rewards.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 6, 44, 2, 41, 41, 'great multitude of fishes', 'Connection of Abundant Gathering', 'This connection highlights the theme of abundance in both passages. In Luke, the great multitude of fishes signifies a miraculous catch, while in Acts, the addition of about three thousand souls represents a significant spiritual harvest.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 6, 44, 4, 4, 4, 'great multitude of fishes', 'Connection of Abundance and Belief', 'This connection highlights the theme of abundance leading to belief. In Luke, the great multitude of fishes symbolizes a miraculous provision, while in Acts, the significant number of believers reflects a similar abundance resulting from the preaching of the word.', 'theme', 0.307, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 7, 48, 6, 2, 2, NULL, 'Burden Sharing in Community', 'This connection highlights the theme of mutual support in both passages. In Luke 5:7, the fishermen call for help to manage their overwhelming catch, while Galatians 6:2 emphasizes bearing one another''s burdens, suggesting a communal responsibility.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 7, 50, 4, 3, 3, 'help them', 'Collaboration in Ministry', 'This connection highlights the theme of collaboration in ministry. Both passages emphasize the importance of helping one another in laboring for the gospel.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 7, 44, 11, 25, 25, 'beckoned unto their partners', 'Collaboration in Ministry', 'This connection highlights the theme of collaboration in both passages. In Luke, the fishermen work together to manage their catch, while in Acts, Barnabas seeks Saul to partner in ministry.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
